# Running Verus

The default way to run Verus verification on this project:

```bash
cd ~/projects/APAS-VERUS && ~/projects/verus-lang/source/target-verus/release/verus --crate-type=lib src/lib.rs --multiple-errors 20 --expand-errors
```

Use this command when:
- Checking if code verifies
- After making changes to proofs or implementations
- Before committing changes
